<td class="mbox-text" style=""><a href="/wiki/Wikiquote" title="Wikiquote">Wikiquote</a> has a collection of quotations related to: <i><b><a href="http://en.wikiquote.org/wiki/Special:Search/Alternate_history" class="extiw" title="q:Special:Search/Alternate history">Alternate history</a></b></i></td>
